Class MobileRoboticSimulation

java.lang.Object
simulation.MobileRoboticSimulation
All Implemented Interfaces:
IMobileRoboticSimulation
public class MobileRoboticSimulation extends Object implements IMobileRoboticSimulation
Class that represents a robot simulation
This simulation has two states, a pre start and a post start
Version:
2.0 08/05/2023
Author:
Alexandre Rodrigues, Miguel Cabrita and Afonso Rio
